Managing routes.

The destinations are divided into zones. Each zones has it's zip codes.

Path_code is subset of the zones.

Shipping option contains path_code, date and time of week of delivery (doesn't change every week). [class]

Mission is shipping options for certain week.

Client gives it's zip code -> zone -> can see shipping options.

We need to update the shipping options according the available drivers/cars.

Multi-site: the data will be update in the master and updated to slaves systems.

